## Your Task

Implement `file_append(path, content)` in `stdlib/file.kl` — append string content to an existing file, creating if not exists. (per DESIGN.md section "Standard Library", `stdlib.fs`) Tests should cover: append to existing file, append to non-existent file (creates it), multiple appends accumulate.

